#: includes/admin/class-admin-settings.php:913
msgid "HTML Cache Lifetime"
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-admin-settings.php:913
msgid ""
"0 = no-cache (recommended for HTML). Non-zero values cache HTML in the "
"browser."
msgstr ""

